<font color="#ff00ff">(WHIMPERING)</font>

18:44.860 --> 18:46.930
We can work through this.

18:46.930 --> 18:48.630
Just put the guns away. I...

18:48.630 --> 18:50.000
<font color="#ff00ff">(SPUTTERS)</font>

18:50.000 --> 18:51.370
What's happening?

18:51.370 --> 18:52.930
I didn't do anything.

18:52.940 --> 18:54.570
My name is Barry.

18:54.570 --> 18:56.070
All right?

18:56.070 --> 18:59.140
We have to get Kevin
to stay in the light.

18:59.140 --> 19:01.180
Just-just don't shoot us.

19:01.180 --> 19:03.010
<font color="#138ce9">DR. STAPLE:</font> Don't shoot.

19:03.010 --> 19:05.920
He won't hurt anyone now.

19:07.950 --> 19:10.220
You may find
your way out of here,

19:10.220 --> 19:12.490
but you will have to hurt
a lot of officers.

19:12.490 --> 19:14.160
A lot of people.

19:14.160 --> 19:17.360
No one needs to get hurt
anymore, David.

19:21.630 --> 19:23.970
<font color="#ff00ff">(WIND WHISTLING)</font>

19:29.110 --> 19:32.370
<font color="#138ce9">DAVID:</font> It's gonna be okay, Joseph.

19:32.380 --> 19:33.610
<font color="#138ce9">DR. STAPLE:</font> <font color="#ff00ff">(OVER SPEAKER)</font> Take them straight to

19:33.610 --> 19:37.010
Raven Hill Memorial, the West
Wing of Raven Hill Memorial.

19:37.010 --> 19:39.450
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIRENS WAILING OVER SPEAKER)</font>

19:39.450 --> 19:41.280
<font color="#ff00ff">(FRANTIC SHOUTING OVER SPEAKER)</font>

19:41.290 --> 19:43.090
<font color="#138ce9">MAN:</font> <font color="#ff00ff">(OVER SPEAKER)</font> Grab that poncho!

19:43.090 --> 19:44.920
<font color="#ff00ff">(AUDIO OVER SPEAKER STOPS)</font>

19:45.660 --> 19:48.660
<font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>

19:48.660 --> 19:50.230
<font color="#ff00ff">(SNIFFLES)</font>

19:51.300 --> 19:53.130
<font color="#ff00ff">(ALARM BUZZES)</font>

19:55.000 --> 19:58.000
<font color="#ff00ff">(QUIET CHATTER,
CHAINS CLINKING)</font>

19:58.000 --> 19:59.470
<font color="#138ce9">GUARD:</font> No trouble.

20:04.240 --> 20:06.340
<font color="#ff00ff">(ALARM BUZZES IN DISTANCE)</font>

20:08.550 --> 20:10.210
<font color="#ff00ff">(ALARM BUZZES)</font>

20:11.950 --> 20:13.650
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHEELS SQUEAKING SOFTLY)</font>

20:13.650 --> 20:15.950
<font color="#138ce9">GUARD:</font> Keep moving.

20:16.690 --> 20:18.620
Keep moving.

20:18.620 --> 20:20.090
<font color="#138ce9">HEINRICH:</font> Please, don't. Don't.

20:20.090 --> 20:21.260
- Don't. No.
- Easy. Easy.

20:21.260 --> 20:23.090
- <font color="#ff00ff">(HEINRICH STAMMERS)</font>
- Hey. Hey! Hey!

20:23.090 --> 20:24.730
<font color="#138ce9">HEDWIG:</font> We're cool, we're cool.
Totally cool.

20:24.730 --> 20:26.290
All right?
He doesn't like to be touched.

20:26.300 --> 20:29.130
I can, I can walk.
I'll just, I'll... walk.

20:29.130 --> 20:30.970
<font color="#138ce9">GUARD:</font> Keep walking.

20:36.240 --> 20:38.340
<font color="#ff00ff">(DOOR CLOSES, ALARM BUZZES)</font>

20:43.550 --> 20:45.480
<font color="#ffff00">♪</font>

21:00.200 --> 21:04.070
My name is Dr. Ellie Staple,
and I'm a psychiatrist.

21:06.070 --> 21:08.200
This room must look nefarious.

21:08.210 --> 21:12.070
The walls are equipped with
46 high-pressured nozzles,

21:12.080 --> 21:14.210
all connected
to a 15,000-gallon

21:14.210 --> 21:16.410
water tank outside.

21:16.410 --> 21:18.480
It will only be triggered
if you are threatening

21:18.480 --> 21:20.650
or trying to escape.

21:20.650 --> 21:22.950
This is a hypnosis light...

21:24.760 --> 21:27.020
<font color="#138ce9">DENNIS:</font> Dennis.

21:27.020 --> 21:30.090
My pleasure, Dennis.

21:30.090 --> 21:32.230
You are being monitored.

21:32.230 --> 21:34.100
If, for some reason,
there's a threatening identity

21:34.100 --> 21:36.100
in the room, the light
will automatically strobe

21:36.100 --> 21:38.630
and force a different identity
to take over.

21:38.640 --> 21:40.100
Who was the man?

21:40.100 --> 21:43.370
He was as strong as The Beast.

21:43.370 --> 21:46.110
The man people in this city
have been talking about.

21:46.110 --> 21:48.680
The only person
to survive that train wreck

21:48.680 --> 21:50.550
all those years ago.

21:50.550 --> 21:53.250
<font color="#138ce9">DR. STAPLE:</font> I saw a video of you fighting

21:53.250 --> 21:55.590
near a fire hydrant
that erupted.

21:55.590 --> 21:57.120
Saw you choke.

21:57.120 --> 21:59.790
I think you believe
water is your weakness.

21:59.790 --> 22:01.260
Where are you keeping him?

22:01.260 --> 22:03.360
<font color="#ff00ff">(THE BEAST
GROWLING AND CHUFFING)</font>

22:08.270 --> 22:09.800
<font color="#ff00ff">(YELLING, LIGHTS POPPING
AND HUMMING)</font>

22:09.800 --> 22:12.300
<font color="#ff00ff">(THE BEAST GROANING)</font>

22:14.200 --> 22:16.540
<font color="#138ce9">DR. STAPLE:</font> <i>Everyone is safe, David.</i>

22:16.540 --> 22:22.550
Maybe this will all make sense
if I explain who I am.

22:22.550 --> 22:27.250
I specialize in a particular
type of delusion of grandeur.

22:27.250 --> 22:30.150
I specialize
in those individuals

22:30.150 --> 22:33.090
who believe
they are superheroes.

22:33.090 --> 22:35.090
- <font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>
- I've been given three days

22:35.090 --> 22:38.160
to treat you
by whatever means necessary.

22:39.830 --> 22:43.570
I came here for you both.

22:43.570 --> 22:44.570
<font color="#ff00ff">(THUNDER RUMBLING)</font>

22:44.570 --> 22:47.200
<font color="#ff00ff">(MAN SPEAKING INDISTINCTLY
OVER LOUDSPEAKER)</font>

22:51.210 --> 22:54.080
<font color="#ff00ff">(THUNDER RUMBLING,
RAIN FALLING)</font>

23:09.460 --> 23:11.560
<font color="#138ce9">PIERCE:</font> <i>Yo, this doctor comes in here,</i>

23:11.560 --> 23:14.200
takes over our wing,
tells us all new rules.

23:14.200 --> 23:16.630
- Rules of conduct.
- <font color="#ff00ff">(ROMANTIC JAZZ BALLAD PLAYING)</font>

23:16.630 --> 23:20.300
How to treat people
with kindness.

23:20.300 --> 23:22.740
My whole life, all I do
is take care of people.

23:22.740 --> 23:26.270
Come on, come on, come on,
come on, come on. There you go.

23:26.280 --> 23:28.510
We got along just fine
without her, didn't we?

23:28.510 --> 23:29.850
Me and you?

23:29.850 --> 23:31.850
<font color="#ff00ff">(ELIJAH SIPPING, PIERCE SIGHS)</font>

23:31.850 --> 23:34.750
Anyway...

23:34.750 --> 23:37.750
you won't be lonely anymore.

23:37.760 --> 23:40.320
You have two new friends.

23:40.320 --> 23:43.600
<font color="#ff00ff">(LIVELY CHATTER,
SCHOOL BELL RINGS)</font>

23:50.600 --> 23:53.170
<font color="#ff00ff">(LOCKER OPENS, CLOSES)</font>

23:57.910 --> 23:59.710
<font color="#ff00ff">(TONE BEEPS OVER P.A.)</font>

23:59.710 --> 24:03.180
Casey, could I see you
for a second?

24:10.660 --> 24:13.320
<i>I received a call
from your foster family.</i>

24:13.320 --> 24:16.660
Apparently, it's on the news.

24:16.660 --> 24:19.430
They caught the guy
who abducted you

24:19.430 --> 24:22.200
and murdered all those girls.

24:22.200 --> 24:23.930
They caught the bastard.

24:23.940 --> 24:26.470
Your foster family is thrilled.

24:26.470 --> 24:30.540
I can imagine how much relief
this causes you.

24:30.540 --> 24:33.280
I'm sure you've been
thinking about him.

24:35.680 --> 24:39.150
I... have been
thinking about him.

24:42.520 --> 24:43.720
<font color="#ff00ff">(SCANNER BEEPS)</font>

24:48.290 --> 24:50.160
<font color="#ff00ff">(ALARM BUZZES, LOCK CLICKS)</font>

24:53.970 --> 24:56.970
<font color="#ff00ff">(JADE SIGHS)</font>

24:56.970 --> 25:00.300
They, uh, told me to bring
lots of options.

25:00.300 --> 25:02.970
<font color="#ff00ff">(JADE CHUCKLES)</font>

25:02.970 --> 25:05.180
Hey, cutie.

25:06.880 --> 25:09.280
Think you could help me?

25:09.280 --> 25:10.750
I'm Jade.

25:10.750 --> 25:13.850
They gave me a syringe for
my diabetes, but I dropped it.

25:13.850 --> 25:16.550
My hands get shaky
when I get low blood sugar.

25:16.550 --> 25:18.550
It's a little too close
to the light.

25:18.560 --> 25:21.660
Do you think you could
pick it up for me?

25:32.340 --> 25:35.740
<font color="#ff00ff">(JADE CHUCKLES)</font>

25:35.740 --> 25:38.840
Wow.

25:38.840 --> 25:40.410
Stand up.

25:40.410 --> 25:43.510
Let me get a good look at you.

25:49.390 --> 25:51.750
You are so tall.

25:51.760 --> 25:56.030
Orwell and Barry are so angry
with me that I flipped.

25:56.030 --> 25:58.690
But the truth is

25:58.700 --> 26:02.770
we really can do things
that you can't do.

26:02.770 --> 26:05.640
- I don't understand.
- <font color="#ff00ff">(CHUCKLES)</font>

26:08.840 --> 26:09.810
<font color="#ff00ff">(LIGHTS POPPING)</font>

26:11.740 --> 26:14.340
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTING)</font>

26:14.340 --> 26:15.850
<font color="#ff00ff">(IAN GROANING)</font>

26:18.480 --> 26:20.980
<font color="#138ce9">IAN:</font> Hey. Hey. Hey!

26:20.990 --> 26:23.050
<font color="#ff00ff">(IAN GROANS)</font>

26:23.050 --> 26:25.650
I'm Ian.

26:25.660 --> 26:28.760
All right?
<font color="#ff00ff">(COUGHS)</font> I'm Ian.

26:28.760 --> 26:31.690
<font color="#138ce9">MARY:</font> And I'm Mary Reynolds.
We're twins.

26:31.700 --> 26:33.630
Do you know
what would have happened

26:33.630 --> 26:36.070
if she'd have gotten
to that key, you gobshite?

26:36.070 --> 26:37.830
The Horde would have killed ya.

26:37.840 --> 26:39.400
<font color="#138ce9">IAN:</font> What've you got?

26:39.400 --> 26:41.970
You get a little,
get a little hard-on? Daryl.

26:41.970 --> 26:44.370
Just calm down, okay?

26:44.370 --> 26:46.480
<font color="#ff00ff">(LIGHTS POPPING AND HUMMING,
IAN GROANS)</font>

26:46.480 --> 26:49.110
<font color="#138ce9">NORMA:</font> I'm sorry
for being with the Horde.

26:49.110 --> 26:51.110
It's just, it's just...

26:51.120 --> 26:53.750
Oh, do you know,
I am tired of being sorry.

26:53.750 --> 26:55.720
You can call me Norma.
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIGHS)</font>

26:55.720 --> 26:57.950
I am sorry about
the whole lying thing.

26:57.960 --> 27:00.090
- Though I'm not lying.
- Bro, just stop talking!

27:00.090 --> 27:01.420
<font color="#ff00ff">(GROANING)</font>

27:01.430 --> 27:03.730
<font color="#138ce9">JALIN:</font> I was so amped!

27:03.730 --> 27:06.360
We almost got you, bro!
<font color="#ff00ff">(LAUGHS)</font>

27:06.360 --> 27:08.460
Trying to keep him here
with this light thing?

27:08.470 --> 27:11.670
- That's some buttery shit!
- Stop talking.

27:12.970 --> 27:15.440
<font color="#138ce9">ANSEL:</font> <font color="#ff00ff">(GROANS)</font> I'm not
supposed to be in the light.

27:15.440 --> 27:17.540
Uh, we need more time.

27:17.540 --> 27:19.370
<font color="#ff00ff">(STAMMERS)</font> Barry is
speaking to Kevin,

27:19.380 --> 27:20.940
trying to get him
near the light.

27:20.950 --> 27:22.580
Is he close enough yet?

27:24.820 --> 27:28.980
- <font color="#138ce9">B.T.:</font> The only one who can defend us is him!
- <font color="#ff00ff">(HITS TABLE)</font>

27:28.990 --> 27:30.450
Him!

27:30.450 --> 27:32.450
<font color="#ff00ff">(B.T. GROANS)</font>

27:32.460 --> 27:34.590
<font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>

27:44.870 --> 27:48.040
<font color="#138ce9">PATRICIA:</font> Where is the man
in the rain poncho?

27:48.040 --> 27:51.470
Who is he?

27:51.480 --> 27:55.440
Is he just a regular man?
I need to know.

27:55.450 --> 27:57.080
<font color="#ff00ff">(DARYL PANTING)</font>

27:57.080 --> 28:00.480
All right, step away from
the controls now, little duck.

28:00.480 --> 28:03.350
That's fine.
Now just walk away.

28:06.160 --> 28:08.460
<font color="#ff00ff">(SCANNER BEEPS, ALARM BUZZES)</font>

28:10.800 --> 28:13.960
- <font color="#ff00ff">(ALARM BUZZES, LOCK CLICKS)</font>
- That's it.

28:13.970 --> 28:15.900
Just tiptoe away.

28:18.170 --> 28:21.170
I try to come once every week.

28:21.170 --> 28:22.840
Sometimes, I admit,

28:22.840 --> 28:25.510
I have neglected a week
here and there.

28:25.510 --> 28:29.910
He's changed over the years.

28:29.910 --> 28:33.050
I can tell he's given up.

28:33.050 --> 28:36.050
It's hard to see.

28:36.050 --> 28:38.920
He thinks he was a mistake.

28:38.920 --> 28:41.490
I'm not saying
he did good things.

28:41.490 --> 28:42.930
He didn't.

28:42.930 --> 28:46.530
Those poor people didn't
deserve to die like that.

28:48.070 --> 28:52.600
But he's trying
to make sense of who he is.

28:52.600 --> 28:54.670
Ain't we all doing that?

28:55.910 --> 28:57.710
Yes, ma'am, we are.

29:00.780 --> 29:03.510
They keep him heavily sedated.

29:03.510 --> 29:06.050
This is an enormous amount
of sedation.

29:06.050 --> 29:07.950
He's too smart for 'em.

29:07.950 --> 29:09.950
When they first
brought him here,

29:09.950 --> 29:12.960
he memorized a blueprint
left out from an electrician

29:12.960 --> 29:17.430
and short-circuited the power
to the whole hospital.

29:18.960 --> 29:21.530
He's good
thinking through things.

29:23.230 --> 29:25.570
He has this notion

29:25.570 --> 29:29.610
that superheroes are
based on people like him,

29:29.610 --> 29:33.710
and that other gentleman
I read is here, Mr. Dunn.

29:33.710 --> 29:35.710
Would it surprise you to know

29:35.710 --> 29:39.880
there are more and more people
who have this delusion?

29:39.880 --> 29:43.620
It is actually
the center of my work.

29:43.620 --> 29:46.960
Yes, it would.

29:46.960 --> 29:49.060
<font color="#ff00ff">(ROMANTIC JAZZ BALLAD PLAYING
QUIETLY OVER SPEAKERS)</font>

29:50.960 --> 29:54.070
<font color="#138ce9">MRS. PRICE:</font> You don't let them
get you down, Elijah.

29:55.270 --> 29:57.570
You hear me?

29:58.270 --> 30:00.270
Stay proud.

30:00.270 --> 30:03.610
<font color="#ffff00">♪ As I do</font>

30:03.610 --> 30:07.880
<font color="#ffff00">♪ I never dreamed
that skies... </font><font color="#ffff00">♪</font>

30:07.880 --> 30:08.980
<font color="#ff00ff">(KNOCK ON DOOR)</font>

30:08.980 --> 30:11.080
Step back
against the wall, please.

30:13.150 --> 30:14.820
<font color="#ff00ff">(SCANNER BEEPS, ALARM BUZZES)</font>

30:16.590 --> 30:17.690
<font color="#ff00ff">(ALARM BUZZES)</font>

30:21.090 --> 30:23.530
<font color="#ffff00">♪</font>

30:28.730 --> 30:30.840
<font color="#ff00ff">(BIRDS CAWING IN DISTANCE)</font>

30:33.000 --> 30:34.640
<font color="#ff00ff">(ALARM BEEPING
AND BUZZING QUIETLY)</font>

30:34.640 --> 30:36.640
<font color="#ff00ff">(WATER TANK BEGINS WHIRRING)</font>

30:36.640 --> 30:38.740
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHIRRING GROWS LOUDER)</font>

30:43.250 --> 30:45.550
<font color="#ff00ff">(WATER GURGLING)</font>

30:55.230 --> 30:57.060
<font color="#ff00ff">(DAVID COUGHING)</font>

31:01.770 --> 31:04.200
<font color="#ff00ff">(DOOR OPENS, DAVID PANTING)</font>

31:04.200 --> 31:06.540
<font color="#ff00ff">(WATER DRIPPING)</font>

31:08.940 --> 31:10.810
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTS)</font>

31:13.740 --> 31:16.080
You're keeping him here
without guards?

31:16.080 --> 31:18.810
I have to get out of here
before he gets out.

31:18.820 --> 31:22.150
The individual
who came with you is contained.

31:23.990 --> 31:25.950
David.

31:25.960 --> 31:29.960
I would like you to agree
to have an MRI.

31:29.960 --> 31:32.330
You were the sole survivor of
a devastating train derailment

31:32.330 --> 31:33.800
19 years ago.

31:33.800 --> 31:35.960
It is possible that there was

31:35.970 --> 31:38.770
damage to the frontal lobe
that you are unaware of.

31:41.070 --> 31:42.810
<font color="#ff00ff">(DAVID GRUNTS SOFTLY)</font>

31:44.710 --> 31:46.840
<font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>

31:55.390 --> 31:57.050
Look at you, David.

31:57.050 --> 32:00.060
You believe you have barely
enough strength to stand up.

32:00.060 --> 32:02.890
You can't possibly
explain everything away.

32:04.800 --> 32:07.260
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTING, LIGHTS POPPING)</font>

32:07.260 --> 32:09.730
<font color="#ff00ff">(MR. PRITCHARD PANTING)</font>

32:09.730 --> 32:12.730
Madam, I am Mr. Pritchard.

32:12.740 --> 32:14.870
I'm a professor of cinema.

32:14.870 --> 32:17.710
Specifically, Japanese,
1950s through the 1980s.

32:17.710 --> 32:20.740
And I have absolutely no idea
what I'm doing here. <font color="#ff00ff">(PANTS)</font>

32:20.740 --> 32:22.880
I am very much in favor
of Kevin's reemergence,

32:22.880 --> 32:25.880
and yet I find myself
in a goddamn prison cell!

32:25.880 --> 32:28.020
And I can assure you
I am not...

32:28.020 --> 32:29.720
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTING)</font>

32:29.720 --> 32:31.850
<font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>

32:31.860 --> 32:33.990
<font color="#138ce9">HEDWIG:</font> Okay.

32:33.990 --> 32:35.690
<font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>

32:35.690 --> 32:36.790
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTING)</font>

32:38.730 --> 32:40.900
<font color="#ff00ff">(FELIDA PANTING)</font>

32:40.900 --> 32:43.030
<font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING, SPEAKING SPANISH)</font>

32:53.280 --> 32:55.480
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTING ANGRILY)</font>

32:55.480 --> 32:57.180
<font color="#138ce9">HEDWIG:</font> I'm ready.

32:57.180 --> 32:58.480
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTING)</font>

32:58.480 --> 33:01.820
- Young man, wait!
- <font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>

33:01.820 --> 33:04.420
You will not be able
to get to the light.

33:04.420 --> 33:07.020
It is set off by distance

33:07.020 --> 33:09.320
as well as being monitored
by a camera.

33:09.330 --> 33:12.460
I know this seems
very unfair to you...

33:12.460 --> 33:13.860
<font color="#ff00ff">(BLOWS RASPBERRIES)</font>

33:13.860 --> 33:15.860
...but you are stuck
in this room.

33:15.870 --> 33:18.370
The guy The Beast fought,
he's right there!

33:18.370 --> 33:21.370
<font color="#ff00ff">(PANTING)</font>
He can't beat The Beast.

33:21.370 --> 33:24.940
He doesn't think he can
beat The Beast, does he? Huh?

33:24.940 --> 33:26.340
Beast like...
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTS FIERCELY)</font>

33:26.340 --> 33:29.680
<font color="#ff00ff">(HEDWIG GRUNTS, PANTING)</font>

33:31.220 --> 33:35.080
He doesn't think he can
beat The Beast, does he?

33:35.090 --> 33:38.050
Beast like...
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTS WEAKLY)</font>

33:38.060 --> 33:41.890
Your name is Hedwig, right?

33:41.890 --> 33:44.330
You're nine, right?

33:44.330 --> 33:46.160
Yeah.

33:46.160 --> 33:48.000
Forever?

33:48.000 --> 33:50.130
<font color="#ff00ff">(SIGHS)</font>

33:50.130 --> 33:53.240
No matter how many
experiences you have?

33:56.540 --> 33:58.840
That must be so hard.

34:00.980 --> 34:02.380
You treat people who think

34:02.380 --> 34:04.850
they're comic book characters
or something?

34:07.280 --> 34:09.120
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)</font>

34:09.120 --> 34:11.449
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHUCKLES)</font>

34:11.460 --> 34:13.260
I got to go.

34:13.260 --> 34:16.130
Miss Patricia says
she wants the light.

34:28.409 --> 34:30.870
Hello, Patricia.

