It's just this,
plus an anchoring incident,

52:09.300 --> 52:13.470
and you would have the pattern
for this disorder that I treat.

52:13.470 --> 52:15.810
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHAINS RATTLING SOFTLY)</font>

52:24.950 --> 52:27.950
I hate to see you like this.

52:27.950 --> 52:30.020
This is not
how I would've done things.

52:30.020 --> 52:34.090
I don't approve of
how they've handled you.

52:34.090 --> 52:36.090
Elijah, because of
your condition,

52:36.090 --> 52:38.460
I didn't have to do
an MRI on you.

52:38.460 --> 52:40.630
There are a few in your file.

52:40.630 --> 52:42.630
You definitely have
one of the markers

52:42.630 --> 52:44.500
for this disorder, Elijah.

52:44.500 --> 52:46.200
As do you, Kevin.

52:48.510 --> 52:50.310
These are the medical reasons

52:50.310 --> 52:53.080
I'm thinking
you have this disorder.

52:53.080 --> 52:56.010
Now let's deal with
why you think you don't.

52:56.010 --> 53:01.920
How do you know who's good
and who's bad, David?

53:01.920 --> 53:04.020
Convince me.

53:06.990 --> 53:09.260
It's a feeling.

53:09.260 --> 53:10.690
An intuition?

53:10.700 --> 53:13.660
When you see someone?

53:13.670 --> 53:15.600
I have to touch them.

53:15.600 --> 53:18.470
What does the intuition
feel like?

53:20.540 --> 53:23.440
A vision.

53:23.440 --> 53:25.610
A moment.

53:25.610 --> 53:28.080
A sin.

53:28.080 --> 53:31.350
You kind of
have to interpret it.

53:31.350 --> 53:34.020
Have you ever seen
very good magicians, David?

53:34.020 --> 53:37.290
I mean, the very best.

53:37.290 --> 53:39.190
They are trained as mentalists,

53:39.190 --> 53:42.630
and they can do
seemingly extraordinary feats.

53:42.630 --> 53:45.560
They accomplish these feats by
interpreting hundreds of cues

53:45.560 --> 53:49.430
that an individual is
giving off in a split second.

53:49.430 --> 53:54.340
I think you are like these
professional guessers, David.

53:54.340 --> 53:59.310
You are world-class at it,
simply extraordinary at it.

53:59.310 --> 54:04.750
But it is based on real things,
and you are making the picture.

54:04.750 --> 54:08.250
It is not coming to you
through mystical means.

54:15.460 --> 54:17.630
These are the clothes
that the patient next to you

54:17.630 --> 54:19.460
came in with when he arrived.

54:19.460 --> 54:22.600
There's red clay
staining the pants.

54:22.600 --> 54:25.200
It's very visible.

54:25.200 --> 54:28.500
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHAINS RATTLE SOFTLY)</font>

54:28.510 --> 54:32.510
Is it possible that you saw
something on the news...

54:32.510 --> 54:35.580
- Sorry, bro.
- <i>...then saw an adult acting like a child,</i>

54:35.580 --> 54:39.620
someone who fit the bill
of someone with this disorder,

54:39.620 --> 54:43.020
intuited, "This might be
the person I'm looking for"?

54:43.020 --> 54:44.220
Saw the red clay

54:44.220 --> 54:49.590
and thought he might be hiding
in a place with red clay?

54:49.590 --> 54:51.590
No.

54:51.600 --> 54:54.230
You're certain?

54:55.800 --> 55:00.270
You're... creating a chain of
thoughts that never happened.

55:01.670 --> 55:04.980
<font color="#ff00ff">(PATRICIA CHUCKLES)</font>

55:08.110 --> 55:11.380
You really dissected him,
Doctor.

55:11.380 --> 55:13.750
Good for you.

55:13.750 --> 55:16.590
<font color="#138ce9">DR. STAPLE:</font> As I understand it,
there were many videos

55:16.590 --> 55:18.420
of world-class rock climbers

55:18.420 --> 55:21.190
on the computer
in your office at the zoo.

55:21.190 --> 55:23.530
It was kind of an obsession.

55:23.530 --> 55:25.460
Some of those climbers

55:25.460 --> 55:28.830
could actually scale
a literal wall, couldn't they?

55:28.830 --> 55:31.130
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHUCKLES SOFTLY)</font>

55:31.130 --> 55:32.700
What's your point, Doctor?

55:32.700 --> 55:34.270
It was a practical observation

55:34.270 --> 55:37.540
that produced a practical
skill set in an alter.

55:37.540 --> 55:40.740
Mm.

55:40.750 --> 55:43.550
Then how did he bend the bars?

55:43.550 --> 55:46.250
The iron bars at the zoo?

55:46.250 --> 55:50.220
You did see those, didn't you?

55:50.220 --> 55:51.790
That's not in our heads.

55:51.790 --> 55:53.390
The cages beneath the zoo

55:53.390 --> 55:56.560
were made in 1874
when the zoo first opened.

55:56.560 --> 56:00.260
I was able to bend them by
putting a wrench between them

56:00.260 --> 56:01.400
and leaning back.

56:01.400 --> 56:05.540
Difficult, again, but possible.

56:05.540 --> 56:07.500
No.

56:07.510 --> 56:09.300
What about the shotgun?

56:09.310 --> 56:11.440
He was shot.
Not once but twice.

56:11.440 --> 56:13.440
What does your sleeping mind
think of that?

56:13.440 --> 56:15.780
We've analyzed the shotgun
and the cartridges.

56:15.780 --> 56:17.380
They were very old.

56:17.380 --> 56:20.450
There was a lot of moisture
from the boiler room

56:20.450 --> 56:23.220
down in the locker area
where they were kept.

56:23.220 --> 56:25.720
The cartridges were
possibly compromised.

56:25.720 --> 56:29.220
And some of the pellets
hit the inside of the bars.

56:29.230 --> 56:31.690
<font color="#ff00ff">(PATRICIA CHUCKLES)</font>

56:31.700 --> 56:33.530
It is at least possible

56:33.530 --> 56:36.470
that there is a practical
explanation for this.

56:38.140 --> 56:40.140
<font color="#ff00ff">(GRUNTS SOFTLY)</font>

56:41.710 --> 56:45.610
What if I suggested
something upsetting, Patricia?

56:47.480 --> 56:51.780
Like The Beast isn't
as powerful as you think.

56:51.780 --> 56:56.490
He's not much more powerful
than a strong man.

56:56.490 --> 57:00.190
The facts you are basing
your belief in are wrong.

57:02.760 --> 57:07.630
If superheroes exist, why are
there only three of you?

57:12.600 --> 57:14.740
<font color="#ff00ff">(ELECTRONIC DANCE MUSIC PLAYING
OVER STORE SPEAKERS)</font>

57:14.740 --> 57:17.410
<font color="#138ce9">CASEY:</font> <i>When was the first
comic book written?</i>

57:17.410 --> 57:21.740
The first reprints of newspaper
strips in tabloid size

57:21.750 --> 57:23.680
happened in 1929.

57:23.680 --> 57:28.520
And then, in 1938,
the apotheosis happened.

57:28.520 --> 57:30.790
Action Comics Number One
launched

57:30.790 --> 57:34.390
with the man in the cape and
the blue tights on the cover.

57:34.390 --> 57:35.360
Boo-yah!

57:35.360 --> 57:37.390
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHUCKLES)</font>:{\c} Here we are.

57:37.390 --> 57:39.500
<font color="#ff00ff">(ELECTRONIC DANCE MUSIC
CONTINUES OVER SPEAKERS)</font>

57:44.500 --> 57:46.440
Thank you.

57:51.270 --> 57:53.740
What are you doing back there?

57:53.750 --> 57:56.340
You're not one of those
Hello Kitty pervs?

57:56.350 --> 57:58.720
<font color="#138ce9">JOSEPH:</font> I'm just looking for something.

58:00.790 --> 58:03.550
Prove to someone I'm not crazy.

58:03.550 --> 58:05.520
I'm leaving.

