01:01:08.740 --> 01:01:10.680
Hello?

01:01:26.590 --> 01:01:28.460
<font color="#ff00ff">(SCANNER BEEPS, ALARM BUZZES)</font>

01:01:52.180 --> 01:01:56.190
If, by mistake,
I-I drop this...

01:01:56.190 --> 01:01:59.620
heavy flashlight
on your paper legs...

01:02:01.990 --> 01:02:04.630
...no one would come
check on you for some time,

01:02:04.630 --> 01:02:07.700
not until Daryl gets here
