01:02:13.600 --> 01:02:16.870
Have you been getting
out of your room, Elijah?

01:02:33.560 --> 01:02:35.530
<font color="#ff00ff">(PIERCE PANTING)</font>

01:02:44.500 --> 01:02:47.610
I must be losing my mind.

01:02:57.580 --> 01:02:59.720
<font color="#ff00ff">(TRAIN HORN BLOWING
IN DISTANCE)</font>

01:03:04.990 --> 01:03:06.920
<font color="#ff00ff">(CAR BACKFIRES)</font>

01:03:07.830 --> 01:03:10.030
<font color="#ff00ff">(WHEELS SQUEAKING SOFTLY)</font>

01:03:13.970 --> 01:03:15.700
- <font color="#ff00ff">(KEYS JINGLING)</font>
- <font color="#138ce9">PIERCE:</font> Night, Joe.

01:03:15.700 --> 01:03:17.800
<font color="#138ce9">JOE:</font> Have a good night.

01:03:22.610 --> 01:03:25.140
- Daryl.
- Hey, my man.

01:03:25.140 --> 01:03:26.740
You almost made it.

01:03:26.740 --> 01:03:30.010
<font color="#ff00ff">(CHUCKLES)</font>
I think your watch is fast.

01:03:30.010 --> 01:03:31.280
Joe, my man.

01:03:31.280 --> 01:03:32.780
- How's it going?
- What's going on?

01:03:32.780 --> 01:03:34.220
- What's happening?
- Looking tired, man.

01:03:34.220 --> 01:03:35.580
You still taking
that multivitamin?

01:03:35.590 --> 01:03:36.520
Not like I should.

01:03:36.520 --> 01:03:38.620
Yeah, but, listen,
you got to take the D.

01:03:38.620 --> 01:03:39.690
If you don't take vitamin D,

01:03:39.690 --> 01:03:41.890
none of that stuff's gonna
absorb into your body.

01:03:41.890 --> 01:03:43.790
<font color="#ffff00">♪</font>

